ng colour for\nthe solar cylinder is V-K=2.89 mag compared to the local value of V-K = 2.46\nmag. An extrapolation of the local surface brightness to the whole Milky Way\nyields a total luminosity of M_K = -24.2 mag. The Milky Way falls in the range\nof K band Tully-Fisher (TF) relations from the literature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Apr 2015 13:58:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-06"}
